in case the font is too small, it may have to do with a high resolution screen, in that case
paste this into ~/.Xresources


Xft.dpi: 96

! These might also be useful depending on your monitor and personal preference:
Xft.autohint: 0
Xft.lcdfilter:  lcddefault
Xft.hintstyle:  hintfull
Xft.hinting: 1
Xft.antialias: 1
Xft.rgba: rgbft.dpi: 120
